text: Harry Coker is an American lawyer and national security expert. He has been the acting Maryland Secretary of Commerce since 2025. He was the National Cyber Director from 2023 to 2025 and as the executive director of the National Security Agency from 2017 to 2019. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Lawyers from Maryland Category:Politicians from Maryland Category:Independent politicians in the United States
title: Harry Coker
